## Installation

```bash
# From local development
hermes skills install ~/.hermes/skills/official/mlops/hermetic

# Or from hermetic repo
hermes skills install ~/dev/hermetic

# Enable plugin
hermes plugins enable hermetic
```

## Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `hermes hermetic import` | Import and curate chat exports |
| `hermes hermetic curate` | Run curation on normalized data |
| `hermes hermetic train` | Train LoRA adapter |
| `hermes hermetic status` | Show training artifacts |

## Usage

### Import & Curate

```bash
# Auto-detect platform, curate, output ShareGPT
hermes hermetic import ~/exports/chatgpt.json --curate

# Explicit platform
hermes hermetic import ~/exports/claude.json --platform claude --curate

# Output DPO format
hermes hermetic import ~/exports/gemini/ --format dpo --curate
```

### Train

```bash
# Local MLX (Apple Silicon)
hermes hermetic train ./data --model mlx-community/Qwen3-8B-4bit --lora-layers 4

# Cloud (Modal)
hermes hermetic train ./data --backend unsloth-modal --model "unsloth/Qwen3-8B-bnb-4bit"

# Incremental (merge with previous adapter)
hermes hermetic train ./data --incremental --previous-adapter ./output/adapters
```

### Status

```bash
hermes hermetic status ./output
```

Output example (text):

```text
output_dir: ./output
exists: true
artifacts:
  - type: adapter
    path: ./output/adapters
    has_weights: true
    has_config: true
  - type: gguf
    path: ./output/gguf
    files: 1
metadata:
  model: mlx-community/Qwen3-8B-4bit
  backend: mlx-tune
  config: lora_r=16, lora_alpha=32, lora_layers=4
  metrics: training_time_sec=1240, steps=1000
```

## Skill

The plugin bundles a skill accessible via:

```bash
# View skill
skill_view("hermetic:hermetic")

# Or in-agent
/skill hermetic
```

## Configuration

### Via hermetic.yaml

```text
import:
  sources:
    - path: "~/exports/chatgpt/conversations.json"
    - path: "~/exports/claude/conversations.json"

curate:
  deduplicate:
    enabled: true
    exact_match: true
    semantic_threshold: 0.95
  pii_redact:
    enabled: true
  quality:
    enabled: true

format:
  primary: "sharegpt"
  also: ["dpo", "grpo"]

train:
  backend: "mlx-tune"
  model: "mlx-community/Qwen3-8B-4bit"
  lora:
    r: 16
    alpha: 32
    target_modules: ["q_proj", "v_proj"]
    layers: 4

output:
  formats: ["mlx_adapters", "gguf_4bit"]
  ollama:
    enabled: true
    tag: "hermetic:latest"
```

### Via Config File

```bash
hermes hermetic import -c hermetic.yaml
hermes hermetic train -c hermetic.yaml
```

## Pipeline Integration

```text
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
|                    Hermes Agent Session                     |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
|  hermes hermetic import ~/exports/chatgpt.json --curate    |
|  > Normalized 1,247 conversations                           |
|  > Curated: 1,134 remain (9.1% removed)                    |
|  > Output: ./hermetic-output/sharegpt/                     |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
                              |
                              V
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
|  hermes hermetic train ./hermetic-output                    |
|  > MLX LoRA training on Apple Silicon                      |
|  > Adapter: ./hermetic-output/adapters/                    |
|  > GGUF: ./hermetic-output/gguf/                           |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
                              |
                              V
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
|  Ollama serve + Hermes Gateway hot-swap                     |
|  hermes model load-adapter ./hermetic-output/adapters      |
+-------------------------------------------------------------+
```

